cli/registry.go exports var Registry = map[string]commands.Command{...} mapping command names to Command instances. Commands needing embedded content (help text, skill guide, init template) receive it via struct fields set at Registry construction time. Provides derived helpers subcommandHelp(name) (returns cmd.Meta().Usage) and recognizedFlagsFor(cmd) (builds map from cmd.Meta().Flags). The rejectUnknownFlags function uses recognizedFlagsFor. See <ref spec="output_intent.metadata_single_source">metadata single source</ref>.